import React , { useState , useEffect }from 'react' import { getUser } from "../service/api"; import { Table, TableHead, TableCell, TableRow, TableBody, Button, styled } from '@mui/material' const AllUsers = () => { const [userDetails, setUserDetails]= useState([]) useEffect(()=>{ getUserDetails() },[]) const getUserDetails=async ()=>{ let responce =await getUser() console.log("responce",responce) setUserDetails(responce.data) } return ( <> Id name UserName Email Phone Id {userDetails.name} {userDetails.UserName} {userDetails.Email} {userDetails.Phone}
) } export default AllUsers
